{"tid":1783644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【願還錢歸本人】比個波台狗借左錢唔還，有乜辦法追？","createTime":"2019-12-15T04:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T15:30:05.000Z","uid":24638,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"12ca85f6a1b3d379342a8d334eb17400bddee91e","tid":1783644,"uid":24638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"一個月比晒屋企，得實在唔知從何說起了.....<br />\n同個波台狗由高登識到而家都差唔多十年....<br />\n不嬲都覺得佢無份人無乜點....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日個波台狗whatsapp我，話想我幫佢買個耳機，<br />\n咁我諗住都識左咁耐，唔會呃我掛，<br />\n咪幫佢買囉，買左二千幾，點知佢一手就拎走....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑笑口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跑左去....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好有禮貌咁問佢幾時比我呀，係咪手緊呀...<br />\n佢又唔覆...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實本身都知佢有去開鴨店既習慣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有問呢排d仔係咪好正，用晒d錢呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都唔覆...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日就係payme十幾廿蚊比我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，我有兩個小朋友要養，成家一家之主，<br />\n每個月一出糧就比晒老婆，每個月得$2500，<br />\n但買耳機都比左$2480，得返$120...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家每日就係F5個PAYME，到底幾時先還夠一餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢三日得$49，飯又無得食，<br />\n又怕老婆鬧我，怕佢話我on9上波台識人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位手足有乜辦法追到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係飯都無得食了........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c071dd387e9d508836c124d6e219dea1b6d4836","tid":1783644,"uid":886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddDwBMV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddDwBMV.gif&h=a5f08719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a7c3b74ccebebd6fbd6b42258ca0ddbd9ffb218","tid":1783644,"uid":886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euMqGdW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuMqGdW.gif&h=20a316c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c507af80651d020ed92c3dd61a45775051496804","tid":1783644,"uid":24638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"樓上ching係咩意思呀請問？"},{"pid":"b863f8722dd7117657b3a3d6bff7bd1a4bbf83fd","tid":1783644,"uid":27605,"like":1,"dislike":0